WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:01.755
Previously on "When Calls the Heart"...

00:01.780 --> 00:03.351
Mr. Bouchard hired me!

00:03.376 --> 00:05.345
The sooner we take care
of our money problem,

00:05.370 --> 00:07.364
the sooner we can start
our life together.

00:07.389 --> 00:08.496
One thing I miss about the city?

00:08.521 --> 00:11.054
The postal service delivers
packages right to your door.

00:11.079 --> 00:12.211
If you see Mr. Bouchard,

00:12.236 --> 00:13.328
can you tell him that
his trunk arrived?

00:13.353 --> 00:14.218
<i>What is it?</i>

00:14.243 --> 00:15.898
<i>Just a nice trunk. Wouldn't ya say?</i>

00:15.923 --> 00:18.390
<i>There's something about this
guy that doesn't sit right.</i>

00:18.626 --> 00:20.810
Nobody means more to me than you do.

00:20.835 --> 00:24.245
Yes, to the possibility of you and me!

00:30.220 --> 00:32.735
<i>We never know how life will turn...</i>

00:33.359 --> 00:35.303
<i>It's been a week since Abigail got word</i>

00:35.328 --> 00:37.960
<i>that her mother had
taken ill back East.</i>

00:38.421 --> 00:40.222
<i>True to her nature,</i>

00:40.247 --> 00:43.826
<i>Abigail wasted no time in
rushing off to care for her.</i>

00:45.095 --> 00:47.887
<i>Abigail is much more than a friend.</i>

00:48.364 --> 00:50.029
<i>She's family...</i>

00:50.167 --> 00:52.876
<i>and I'll miss her and Cody deeply.</i>

00:53.539 --> 00:57.749
<i>We all will, but we must
get by as best we can...</i>

00:59.218 --> 01:01.592
<i>Bill has taken over some
of the responsibilities</i>

01:01.617 --> 01:03.156
<i>in the cafe.</i>

01:03.515 --> 01:08.511
<i>Clara, as busy as she is, has
agreed to help out when she can.</i>

01:09.388 --> 01:12.998
<i>We all keep Abigail and
her family in our prayers</i>

01:13.023 --> 01:15.117
<i>and wish her Godspeed.</i>

01:16.863 --> 01:21.523
<i>In her absence, we must
soldier on, and we will.</i>

01:22.043 --> 01:23.820
<i>We are a community.</i>

01:23.845 --> 01:25.444
<i>We are strong.</i>

01:26.338 --> 01:28.269
<i>We are Hope Valley.</i>

01:30.000 --> 01:36.074
